                                    </div>

                                    <div class="next-step-card">
                                        <div class="step-icon">
                                            <i class="fas fa-code"></i>
                                        </div>
                                        <h4>API Reference</h4>
                                        <p>Explore the REST API endpoints and start building integrations.</p>
                                        <a href="/docs/api" class="btn btn-outline">API Docs</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Quick Tips -->
                            <div class="troubleshooting-section">
                                <h3>Quick Tips</h3>
                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>Database Setup</h4>
                                    <p>The database is automatically created when you first run the server. No manual setup required!</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>Environment Variables</h4>
                                    <p>Make sure to set strong, unique values for <code>SESSION_SECRET</code> and <code>JWT_SECRET</code> in production.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="faq-item">
                                    <h4>First User</h4>
                                    <p>The first user to register automatically becomes the "Owner" with full administrative privileges.</p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="help-link">
                                    <p>
                                        Need help? Check the <a href="https://github.com/Dynamicaaa/Sayonika#readme" target="_blank">full README</a> or
                                        <a href="https://github.com/Dynamicaaa/Sayonika/issues" target="_blank">create an issue</a> on GitHub.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
